# Normalize line endings to LF in the repo (Prettier emits LF; this stops CRLF
# churn from inflating every diff on Windows checkouts and keeps lint-staged/
# Prettier from fighting git's autocrlf).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary/asset types git should never touch.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
